title: Seattle City Council Select Budget Committee Session I 10/21/20

In-person attendance is currently prohibited per the Washington Governor's Proclamation No. 20-28.11, through November 9, 2020. Meeting participation is limited to access by telephone conference line and Seattle Channel online.
